APK of Drm features, including update drm secure timer and receive wap push rights.

This library is pre-built by MediaTek internal.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
DrmProvider.apk updates drm secure timer if settings time change, to ensure drm timer is
synchronized with network timer. It saves drm right when receive wap push.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1. telephony-common.jar
2. framework.jar

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1. mediatek-framework.jar

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'system/framework' folder.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
Ensure drm secure timer is always synchronized with network timer.
